title: Cam Newton to the Patriots: Winners and Losers
itunes:title: Cam Newton to the Patriots: Winners and Losers
description:
A bunker filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal are joined by Mike Garafolo to break down the Patriots new quarterback. The heroes throw out some winners and losers and also discuss the latest fine to the New England Patriots from last season. We wrap the show with 8 o'clock delight to make sure you get all of the latest news around the league.
